    "Thanks for helping LiveWallpaper improve. The information below will be pre-filled into a GitHub issue. **Please review it before posting** — once an issue is created, anyone can read it." : {
      "comment" : "Explainer body in the Report a Bug sheet.",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Thanks for helping LiveWallpaper improve. The information below will be pre-filled into a GitHub issue. **Please review it before posting** — once an issue is created, anyone can read it."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "LiveWallpaper の改善にご協力いただきありがとうございます。下記の情報は GitHub issue に事前入力されます。**投稿前に内容をご確認ください** — issue は誰でも閲覧できます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "感谢帮助 LiveWallpaper 改进。下方信息会预填到 GitHub issue 里。**提交前请检查一遍** — issue 一旦创建任何人都能看到。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "感謝協助 LiveWallpaper 改進。下方資訊會預先填入 GitHub issue。**送出前請先檢查** — issue 一旦建立任何人都能看到。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
