    "When on, all connected displays render one stretched video. When off, each display plays its own copy independently — multi-display sync is not possible." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, all connected displays render one stretched video. When off, each display plays its own copy independently — multi-display sync is not possible."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンにすると、接続されているすべてのディスプレイが 1 本の動画を引き伸ばして表示します。オフにすると、各ディスプレイがそれぞれ独立して再生します（マルチディスプレイ同期は不可）。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，所有连接的显示器渲染一段被拉伸的视频；关闭时，每个显示器各自独立播放——多屏无法同步。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟後，所有連接的螢幕渲染一段被拉伸的影片；關閉時，每個螢幕各自獨立播放——多螢幕無法同步。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, clicks and scrolls reach the wallpaper but desktop icons and the Dock become unclickable. Off lets you use Finder normally." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, clicks and scrolls reach the wallpaper but desktop icons and the Dock become unclickable. Off lets you use Finder normally."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンの場合、クリックとスクロールは壁紙に届きますが、デスクトップアイコンと Dock はクリックできなくなります。オフにすると Finder を通常どおり使用できます。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，鼠标点击与滚动作用于壁纸，但桌面图标和 Dock 将无法点击；关闭则可正常使用 Finder。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟時，點按和捲動會傳到桌布，但桌面圖示和 Dock 將無法點按。關閉則可正常使用 Finder。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, HTML wallpapers open with WebKit's Web Inspector accessible — right-click in a webview wallpaper to inspect. Recommended only when debugging your own content." : {
      "comment" : "Detailed info popover for the Developer Mode toggle.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, HTML wallpapers open with WebKit's Web Inspector accessible — right-click in a webview wallpaper to inspect. Recommended only when debugging your own content."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンにすると、HTML 壁紙で WebKit の Web Inspector が使えるようになります — webview 壁紙を右クリックして要素を検証できます。自作コンテンツのデバッグ時のみ推奨します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，HTML 壁纸会启用 WebKit 的 Web Inspector — 在 webview 壁纸上右键即可检查元素。建议仅在调试自有内容时开启。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟後，HTML 桌布會啟用 WebKit 的 Web Inspector — 在 webview 桌布上按右鍵即可檢查元素。建議僅在除錯自有內容時開啟。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "オンの場合、壁紙の WKWebView はセッションごとに新規開始します。cookies、localStorage、キャッシュは保持されません"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，壁纸的 WKWebView 每次会话都会重新开始——Cookie、localStorage 和缓存不会保留"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟時，桌布的 WKWebView 每次工作階段都會全新啟動；cookies、localStorage 和快取不會保留"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, the wallpaper's WKWebView starts fresh each session — cookies, localStorage, and cache are not persisted." : {
